iconserviceagent(1) General Commands Manual iconserviceagent(1)

NAME

iconservicesagent —
agent responsible for generating icon images from the resources provided in application bundles and by the system.

SYNOPSIS

iconservicesagent

DESCRIPTION

iconservicesagent is used by the system read icon resources such as icns files and generate icon images for display.

FILES

/System/Library/CoreServices/iconservicesagent
executable

SEE ALSO

iconservicesd iconutil
